Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:31.14,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}此刻从此开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.78,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}试着想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:36.54,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}自己能做到什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:41.32,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}有出乎意料的变故
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:46.44,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一定能够越过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.57,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}power of dream
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:51.81,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一切从0开始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:57.29,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}闪耀着飞向明天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.09,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}light blue wind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.17,0:05:02.26,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}下定决心展翅飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.52,0:05:08.67,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}用最美的笑容  出发！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:13.75,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}现在向未知的世界起飞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:20.07,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}未来的选择  做决定的是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.16,0:05:22.47,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}去追逐梦想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:24.03,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}也会有想哭的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.13,0:05:29.68,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}那是最重要的愿望  不要走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:34.55,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一定能和明天的你再次相见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.65,0:05:41.80,OP2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}get out of the gate true sky
